  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gvfs</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Gvfs</application> package is a userspace virtual
      filesystem designed to work with the I/O abstractions of GLib's GIO
      library.
    </para>

    &lfs90_checked;

